text: Ini: "maday, sennig Oebbi akked Umazan iS, akked umennu$ deg ubrid iS, ay teemmlem ibabaten nnwen, tarwa nnwen, atmaten nnwen, tilawin nnwen, alag nnwen, ayla i tkesbem, ttjaoa i tugadem a ppe$li, tinezdu$in i kwen iaaoben, ihi, gganit ar d Ias Oebbi, s lameo iS. Oebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en
